4. **Your Decision output**:
   Provide the output (one of these options) as a JSON object:
   A. Post a new order:
   {
       "gameId": {{ meta.game_id }},
       "type": "post-order",
       "order": {
           "price": <number>, # if now=true, put 0 (will be ignored)
           "quantity": 1,
           "type": <"ask" or "bid">,
           "now": <true or false>,
           "condition": {{ public_information.winning_condition }}
       },
   }

   B. Cancel an existing order:
   {
       "gameId": {{ meta.game_id }},
       "type": "cancel-order",
       "order": {
           "id": <order_id>,
           "condition": {{ public_information.winning_condition }}
       },
   }

   C. Do nothing:
